      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 190,
      "message": "I think we should have the\n```java\n        boolean lockEnabled = Boolean.parseBoolean(\n                Optional.ofNullable(System.getenv(\"AAI_INDEX_LOCK_ENABLED\"))\n                        .orElse(\"false\")\n```\ncheck here and not invoke the method when it is not active.\n\nYou can then remove all the control structures inside the method, which also avoids iterating over all vertex indices (that could potentially be quite a few) when it is not necessary",
